missions/vasseur-pressure/steps/step-002/explorations/exploration-002/GOAL.md:11:**Key finding from exploration-001:** The W^{1,3} threshold is UNIVERSAL. Both the CZ ceiling (u ∈ L^3 → p ∈ L^{3/2}) and BMO control (W^{1,3} ⊂ BMO) require the same borderline Sobolev space. The β = 3/2 threshold and W^{1,3} threshold are two faces of the same obstruction.
