+# L^3 Host-Space Audit for Chain 02 Step 1
+
+## Goal
+
+Audit `L^3` as the candidate host space for Chain 02 Step 1 in
+`beyond-de-giorgi`, using the frozen extraction-package checklist from
+`step-007`.
+
+## Method
